sation and evaporation, thus indicating a distinct dominant\nslow component in the moist stratified two-dimensional turbulent system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2011 11:28:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
